7. Security design
Authentication: JWT (short-lived access token, optional refresh token).

Authorization: Role-based checks at:

API Gateway

Service level (for sensitive operations)

Data isolation:

All queries filtered by church_id from JWT.

Transport security: HTTPS in production.

Password security: bcrypt with strong salt rounds.

